      },
      {
        "id": "PD1.11-publicityCode",
        "path": "PD1.11-publicityCode",
        "short": "Publicity Code",
        "definition": "This field contains a user-defined code indicating what level of publicity is allowed (e.g., No Publicity, Family Only) for the patient. Refer to {{v2-table:0215:Publicity Code}} in Chapter 2C, Code Tables, for suggested values. Refer to _PV2-21 - Visit Publicity Code_ for visit level code.",
